Raw soybean leaves iron-metabolism metrics

Source: R/data-soybean_ir_metrics.R
soybean_ir_metrics.Rd

This data contains metrics for raw RNA-sequencing read counts from a soybean dataset that compared leaves that were exposed to iron-rich (iron-postive) soil conditions versus leaves that were exposed to iron-poor (iron-negative) soil conditions. The data was collected 120 minutes after iron conditions were initiated. The metrics include the log fold change and the p-values for all genes and all pairwise combinations of treatment groups.

Format

a RData instance, 1 list per treatment group combination and 1 row per gene

Details

Raw soybean leaves metrics

  • ID gene name

  • logFC log fold change

  • PValue p-value

See also

soybean_ir for information about the treatment groups
